extends ../layout

block content
  .min-h-screen.flex.items-center.justify-center
    .bg-white.shadow-lg.rounded-lg.p-8.w-full.max-w-md
      h1.text-2xl.font-bold.mb-4
        | Frontend Security Scanner

      p.text-sm.text-gray-600.mb-6
        | Analizá rápidamente la seguridad frontend de un sitio web.
      
      p.text-sm.text-gray-500.mt-4
        | Escaneo gratuito limitado a una prueba por sitio.
      
      form(method="POST", action="/scanner/demoScan", class="space-y-4")
        input(
          type="url"
          name="url"
          required
          placeholder="https://ejemplo.com"
          class="w-full px-4 py-2 border rounded-md focus:outline-none focus:ring"
        )

        button(
          type="submit"
          class="w-full bg-blue-600 text-white py-2 rounded-md hover:bg-blue-700"
        )
          | Analizar sitio
